response.overview: Reckless Youth wrestles Larry Sweeney for his ICW-ICWA Tex-Arkana Television Championship! Former YLC champs Jigsaw and Hallowicked look to settle their differences. International styles are showcased in tag matches featuring both KUDO & Chuichiro Arai, as well as Skayde & Milano Collection AT!
